FROM rust:1.78-bookworm AS chef
WORKDIR /app
RUN cargo install cargo-chef
COPY Cargo.toml Cargo.lock ./
RUN cargo chef prepare --recipe-path recipe.json

FROM rust:1.78-bookworm AS rust-builder
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=chef /app/recipe.json recipe.json
RUN cargo install cargo-chef && \
    cargo chef cook --release --recipe-path recipe.json
COPY server/ ./server/
COPY Cargo.toml Cargo.lock ./
RUN cargo build --release

FROM python:3.11-slim-bookworm AS python-builder
WORKDIR /app
RUN python -m venv /opt/venv
ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH"
RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends build-essential && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
COPY requirements.txt ./
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt

FROM debian:bookworm-slim AS runtime
WORKDIR /app
RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && \
    groupadd -r inference && \
    useradd -r -u 1000 -g inference inference
COPY --from=rust-builder /app/target/release/inference-server /usr/local/bin/inference-server
COPY --from=python-builder /opt/venv /opt/venv
ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH"
RUN chown -R inference:inference /app
USER inference
EXPOSE 8080
LABEL maintainer="ml-inference-team@example.com"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Rust + Python ML inference server with PyO3"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.source="https://github.com/org/ml-inference-server"
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8080/health || exit 1
CMD ["/usr/local/bin/inference-server", "--port", "8080"]
